title: 10 - Caitlin Peluffo

description: You’ve seen her on Colbert, now hear her in your ears! It’s the episode of Caitlins, and this one is with the wonderful Caitlin Peluffo. We talk about everything from misspelling names to hidden identities to secret handshakes. Here’s five words to describe this episode: it certainly crosses the border.
